        <li><strong>Permit Assistance:</strong> We help secure necessary permits and ensure compliance with Deptford and Gloucester County regulations.</li>
        <li><strong>Excavation:</strong> Professional excavation to proper depth, accounting for frost line and soil conditions.</li>
        <li><strong>Formwork & Reinforcement:</strong> Installation of forms and reinforcement (rebar) as specified in the design.</li>
        <li><strong>Concrete Pouring:</strong> Placement of high-quality concrete mix appropriate for pole barn foundation requirements.</li>
        <li><strong>Finishing:</strong> Proper finishing and curing to ensure maximum strength and durability.</li>
        <li><strong>Inspection:</strong> Final inspection to ensure code compliance and quality standards.</li>
      </ol>

